commendations for venues that can accommodate our guest list.</div><div><br></div><div>2. <strong>Guest Count</strong>: We anticipate inviting around [insert number] guests, and we want to ensure that the venue can comfortably accommodate everyone.</div><div><br></div><div>3. <strong>Theme and Style</strong>: We are leaning towards a [insert theme, e.g., rustic, elegant, modern, etc.] theme, with a color palette of [insert colors]. We would love your input on how to best execute this vision through decor, floral arrangements, and overall ambiance.</div><div><br></div><div>4. <strong>Budget</strong>: Our budget for the wedding is approximately [insert budget range]. We would appreciate your guidance on how to allocate our budget effectively across different aspects of the wedding.</div><div><br></div><div>5. <strong>Services Needed</strong>: We are interested in a comprehensive package that includes venue selection, vendor coordination (catering, photography, entertainment, etc.), timeline management, and day-of coordination. If you offer additional services such as design and decor, please let us know.</div><div><br></div><div>6. <strong>Special Considerations</strong>: We have a few special requests, including [insert any specific requests, such as dietary restrictions, cultural traditions, etc.]. We would like to ensure that these are thoughtfully incorporated into our wedding plans.</div><div><br></div><div>We would love to schedule a consultation to discuss our vision in more detail and learn more about your services, including pricing and availability. Please let us know your available times for a meeting, either in person or virtually.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for your time, and we look forward to hearing from you soon!</div><div><br></div><div>Best regards,</div><div><br></div><div>John [Last Name]  </div><div>[Contact Information]  </div><div>[Optional: Wedding Date]  </div>]]></field>
